      "id": "PopularPost220471",
      "post_content": "The rule about needing to distribute lethal damage before assigning damage to other creatures is incredibly annoying in this case and others like the [Kashi-Tribe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kashi-Tribe) and [Matsu-Tribe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Matsu-Tribe). They simply do not function as intended; I thought this was Wizard's prime consideration in changing rules.  \n  \nCan anyone explain why they made this specific change (not damage on the stack)?",
      "posted_by": "djflo",
